name: Self
description: The universe loves you. Find peace, find love, find what you need to feel at home in your life. Trust in the intelligence that has manifested within you, give your spirit the space to reveal its clarity. Do not demand power, and do not deny it when you have it. Love yourself, love everyone else. Life is most precious. This artwork is one of my first, and I used it as my avatar since a couple of years now. It symbolises the ever changing nature of the self.
